## 3. Evidence Requirements

**Every claim must have evidence:**

| Claim | Required Evidence |
|-------|-------------------|
| "File created" | Show file path + content sample |
| "Test passes" | Show test execution output |
| "Error fixed" | Show before/after + no error |
| "API works" | Show request/response |
| "Data correct" | Show actual data samples |

## 4. Confidence Calibration

```
Base: 100%

Deductions:
- Code not tested on real data: -50%
- Artifacts not opened/verified: -40%
- No independent cross-check: -30%
- Assumptions not validated: -25%
- Edge cases not tested: -20%
- No error handling: -15%

Example:
